headline: What Makes IQVIA (IQV) an Attractive Investment?
summary: Artisan Partners, an investment management company, released its “Artisan Select Equity Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund’s Investor Class ARTNX, Advisor Class APDNX, and Institutional Class APHNX returned 6.77%, 6.76%, and 6.80%, respectively, in the second quarter, compared to a 10.94% return for the S&P […]
